org.interledger

インタフェース InterledgerPacket

  • 既知のサブインタフェースのリスト:
    InterledgerPayment, InterledgerProtocolError, QuoteByDestinationAmountRequest, QuoteByDestinationAmountResponse, QuoteBySourceAmountRequest, QuoteBySourceAmountResponse, QuoteLiquidityRequest, QuoteLiquidityResponse, QuoteRequest, QuoteResponse
    既知の実装クラスのリスト:
    InterledgerPayment.AbstractInterledgerPayment, InterledgerProtocolError.AbstractInterledgerProtocolError, QuoteByDestinationAmountResponse.Builder.Impl

    public interface InterledgerPacket

    A top-level interface for all Interledger objects that can be encoded and decoded as an Interledger packet using some sort of encoding, such as ANS.1, JSON, Protobuf or some other encoding. Not all POJOs in this library are considered Interledger "packets". For example, an InterledgerAddress is used in many packet implementations, but is not something that is sent by itself "on the wire" to facilitate Interledger operations. Conversely, InterledgerPayment is an Interledger packet because it is sent by itself "on the wire" to facilitate Interledger operations.
